-----------------
VRaptor archetype
-----------------

Install:
mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=br.com.caelum.vraptor.archetypes -DartifactId=vraptor-hibernate-archetype -Dversion=0.0.1 -Dpackaging=jar -Dfile=vraptor-mongodb-archetype-0.0.1.jar -DgeneratePom=true


Execute:
i)
mvn archetype:generate -DarchetypeGroupId=br.com.caelum.vraptor.archetypes -DarchetypeArtifactId=vraptor-hibernate-archetype -DarchetypeVersion=0.0.1

ii)
mvn -Dwtpversion=1.0 eclipse:eclipse